# AI/ML Internship – Day 8: Generative AI with Stable Diffusion XL

## Overview
Day 8 focused on Generative AI concepts using Stable Diffusion XL (SDXL). The session introduced text-to-image generation, diffusion models, prompt engineering, and image synthesis using pretrained models accelerated with NVIDIA H200 GPUs.

## Topics Covered
- Introduction to Generative AI
- Stable Diffusion XL (SDXL)
- Text-to-Image Generation
- Diffusion Models
- Prompt Engineering
- Image Synthesis
- Hugging Face Diffusers
- GPU-Accelerated Inference

## Practical Learning
- Explored Stable Diffusion XL architecture.
- Generated images from natural language prompts.
- Learned prompt engineering techniques for improving image quality.
- Understood inference workflows using pretrained diffusion models.
- Performed GPU-accelerated image generation.

## Skills Gained
- Generative AI
- Stable Diffusion XL
- Prompt Engineering
- Diffusion Models
- Hugging Face Diffusers
- GPU Inference

## Tools & Libraries
- Python
- PyTorch
- Hugging Face Diffusers
